She is!  At first, though, she was very nervous.  I told her we could start off slow - her dad lives 1 mile from me down a quiet road, so we started driving back and forth between the two houses.
sample.responseB: That's a great idea. It sounds like you have a plan to help her become a confident driver.
sample.responseA: Okay i see well, take your time she will be getting her liscense soon
